data.description: PRICE REDUCED. NO HOA FEES!!! Totally remodeled 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home in Moon Lake Estates. Beautiful, wooded lot with fenced back yard. Open Floor Plan with large eating area in Kitchen. Stone Counter tops and new cabinetry throughout. BATHROOMS REMODELED.  Bring your boat this community has a boat ramp and dock for the beautiful Moon Lake. Picnic area and playground will entertain everyone. PETS ALLOWED, NO RESTRICTIONS ON RENTALS. NO HOA. NO HOA FEES.  Down payment assistance available for qualified buyers Call for lender information for available programs. Assumable qualifying loan available at low percentage rate OF 4.5% WITH FULL PRICE OFFER. Available for Lease, Lease Option or Lease Purchase.
